<P>SERMON, ON THE PRESENT SITUATION OF THE AFFAIRS OF AMERICA AND GREAT-BRITAIN. WRITTEN BY A BLACK, And printed at the Reque&s;t of &s;everal Per&s;ons of di&s;tingui&s;hed CHARACTERS.</P>
