<P>TO THE AMERICANS IN GENERAL, BUT TO THE CITIZENS OF SOUTH-CAROLINA IN PARTICULAR: This &s;mall Tract is DEDICATED, With the greate&s;t Re&s;pect, by Their mo&s;t obedient, And very humble Servant, A Black Whig.</P>
